<h2 id="initial-setup-화면">Initial Setup 화면</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Codiad의 Username과 password는 Linux와 달라도 무방합니다.</li>
  <li><strong><em>단, Path에는 정해진 path를 정확히 입력해주셔야 합니다.</em></strong></li>
</ul>

<h2 id="-2"><img src="/assets/img/codiadsetupimg/initialsetup1.png" alt="initialsetup1" /></h2>
<p><img src="/assets/img/codiadsetupimg/initialsetup2.png" alt="initialsetup2" />
—</p>
<h2 id="folder-name-or-absolute-path-찾기">Folder Name or absolute Path 찾기</h2>

<ul>
  <li>PuTTY / Terminal 접속</li>
  <li>cd public_html/  입력</li>
  <li>Pwd입력</li>
  <li>Path 복사 후 -&gt; 붙여 넣기</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="-3"><img src="/assets/img/codiadsetupimg/absolutepath.png" alt="pathcopy" width="30%" height="30%" /></h2>
